in.ac.iitk.cse.putwb.heuristic

Class BasicSettingsSuggestor

  • java.lang.Object
    • in.ac.iitk.cse.putwb.heuristic.Heuristics
      • in.ac.iitk.cse.putwb.heuristic.DatasetRelatedHeuristics
        • in.ac.iitk.cse.putwb.heuristic.BasicSettingsSuggestor

  • public class BasicSettingsSuggestor
extends DatasetRelatedHeuristics
    Provides suggestions for basic settings (partition size, vertical expense and horizontal expense) for a given dataset, using an approach - "Prefer Privacy" or "Prefer Utility" and waiting time - "Quick", "Normal" or "Thorough".
    By default, the approach is "Prefer Privacy". By default, the waiting time is "Normal".
    Author:
    Saurabh Srivastava
